        <div class="body">
            <p>When you add a issue then you should also provide a reproducable usecase.</p>

<p>Actually all informations are degraded when they can not be detected.
In this case it means that "sr_Latn" would be degraded to "sr".</p>

<p>You should also note that "codesets" are not part of the "language-region" definition which is needed for Zend_Locale.</p>

<p>There is no component within ZF which would accept codesets until now.</p>

